Interactive Bash Utilities
==========================

Provides sane defaults for productive interactive Bash usage.


Files
-----
prompt.sh: A minimal prompt with return code visualization and error description
history.sh: History utilities
ssh.sh: SSH utilities
man.sh: Colorful man pages
misc.sh: Miscellaneous utilities

Usage
-----
Just source the files from your .bashrc:
. ~/bash-utils/prompt.sh
. ~/bash-utils/history.sh
. ~/bash-utils/ssh.sh
. ~/bash-utils/man.sh
. ~/bash-utils/misc.sh

